    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like shine without a single chip or scratch. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, featuring pristine leather upholstery and a factory-fresh scent. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with a smooth engine and precise transmission that have been meticulously cared for. Every feature and electronic component works perfectly, making this a rare find for any discerning buyer seeking a like-new vehicle.",
