    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor door dings, and visible paint thinning on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and clear signs of wear on the driver's seat, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain operational. Mechanically, it runs well and has been regularly serviced, though it may soon require routine maintenance for wear-and-tear items like brake pads or tires. It is a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
